<paragraph blockId="2.[136,1452,1903,1997]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">
<emphasis bold="true" box="[136,257,1903,1925]" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">FIGURE.</emphasis>
<taxonomicName authorityName="Barfod &amp; Heatubun" authorityYear="2022" box="[266,409,1903,1924]" class="Liliopsida" family="Arecaceae" genus="Licuala" kingdom="Plantae" order="Arecales" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="bakeri">
<emphasis box="[266,409,1903,1924]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Licuala bakeri</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
. A. Stem with one leaf left. B. Inflorescence. C. Rachilla with flowers in bud. D. Flower. E. Flower in longitudinal section F. Staminal ring in outside view. G. Fruit H. Fruit in transverse section. Scale bar: A = 
<quantity box="[1172,1234,1939,1961]" metricMagnitude="-1" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.2" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" unit="cm" value="12.0">12 cm</quantity>
, B = 
<quantity box="[1287,1337,1939,1961]" metricMagnitude="-2" metricUnit="m" metricValue="4.0" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" unit="cm" value="4.0">4 cm</quantity>
, C = 
<quantity box="[1389,1448,1939,1961]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="5.0" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" unit="mm" value="5.0">5 mm</quantity>
, D, E = 
<quantity box="[206,282,1975,1997]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.3" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" unit="mm" value="1.3">1.3 mm</quantity>
, F = 
<quantity box="[330,388,1975,1997]" metricMagnitude="-3" metricUnit="m" metricValue="1.0" pageId="2" pageNumber="3" unit="mm" value="1.0">1 mm</quantity>
. A–H from 
<emphasis box="[501,612,1975,1996]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="3">Baker 1059</emphasis>
. Drawn by Lucy T. Smith.
</paragraph>
</caption>
<caption pageId="3" pageNumber="4" startId="3.[136,229,1897,1919]" targetBox="[194,1399,206,1858]" targetPageId="3">
